creator: Redcliffe Labs
descriptionHtml:
Redcliffe Labs is India’s most trusted and fastest growing diagnostics health service provider having its home sample collection service in more than 60 cities with 20+ labs across India. Redcliffe provides various blood tests and full body checkup at the comfort of your home.

Through this easy-to-use app for diagnostic services, you can easily avail full body checkup at home and regular health checkup with easy access to reports at affordable prices. Redcliffe Labs also offers free report consultation so that you consult with qualified doctors from anywhere and get instant solutions to all your health-related queries.

Full body checkup packages at Redcliffe Labs

Smart full body checkup
RT-PCR / COVID test at home
Blood Test
Fever profile with Malaria and Dengue test
Fever panel test
Haemoglobin variant
Healthy heart package
Sugar profile test (Basic and Advanced)
Vitamin profile test
Fever panel with LFT and RT-PCR
Super advance full body checkup female
Super advanced full body checkup male
Arthritis profile package
and others. Through the Redcliffe Labs App, you can also avail home sample collection for various tests such as HbA1c, KFT, Dengue NS1 by ELISA Method, etc.

Stay updated about your health with affordable health checkup packages and get accurate and timely reports with the Redcliffe Labs & Diagnostics App. We also provide people with a personalized diet and nutrition plans with the expert guidance of specialized and verified Nutritionists.

Redcliffe Labs Home sample collection is a service that brings diagnostic services to your doorstep and timely access to reports within same day. Our remote blood test home sample collection promotes safety for both healthcare workers and patients.

We are equipped with healthcare specialists and professional phlebotomists who arrive at your doorstep to collect samples. This service is extremely beneficial during pandemic times and especially for the elderly, bedridden, and patients recovering post-surgeries. Our excellence and standardization programs follow supreme levels of testing expertise and tuning.

At the Redcliffe Labs health test app, you can easily book a home sample collection at home. Our trained and expert phlebotomist will visit your home for sample collection for different health tests. You can access the blood test reports online within 24 hours.

Redcliffe Labs App is your one-stop destination for all diagnostic needs that makes full-body health checkup convenient and affordable. Our healthcare articles or blogs are written by expert medical professionals and you can get complete information about your symptoms and tips to improve your overall health.

Complete body checkup, free report consultations, booking blood tests online, health screening, and other such services are just a click at Redcliffe Labs - one stop solution for all your Diagnostics needs:

Affordable health checkup packages
Safe and convenient home sample collection
Easy payment modes
Timely and accurate reports online
Free report consultation

title: Redcliffe Labs

creator: Redcliffe Labs
descriptionHtml:
For Good Health and Distancing From Health Issues, Timely Preventive Health Checkups are a Must.

Redcliffe Labs- Healthy India’s Trusted Labs introduces a user-friendly Diagnostics App to make health checks convenient with essential home healthcare facilities. This mobile app allows you to opt-in for hassle-free and affordable healthcare services from the comfort of your home.
Redcliffe Labs is a leading diagnostic network with 35+ Labs, 900+ Collection Centers, and 500+ Network Centers. Irrespective of your geographical location, the Redcliffe Labs App makes Health and Wellness accessible for all.
Some of the prominent features of the newly developed Redcliffe Labs App include the below-mentioned features:

Laboratory Services
1) Book a test
2) Opt for a free home sample collection
3) Choose from an extensive range of health services, diagnostic tests, and packages
4) Find a nearby lab
5) Upload the prescription and get consultation assistance from the expert healthcare consultants
6) Live tracking of Phlebotomists
7) Access Lab Test reports online
8) Easy navigation to health-specific categories of packages to get complete information about Routine tests like Diabetes test, Thyroid test, Lipid Profile test, Allergy panel, and Smart Full Body Checkup with RA factor, which comprises 86 test parameters
9) Real-time tracking for home sample collection

Apart from the routine tests, you can also book specialized tests related to Cancer, Genetics, and Pregnancy with Redcliffe Labs App - your trusted healthcare provider.

Some of the popular packages and tests that you can book in 1 minute via the Redcliffe Labs App to get precise Healthcare Solutions are:
1) Smart Full Body Checkup
2) Vital Screening Package
3) Thyroid Test
4) Blood Sugar Test
5) HbA1c
6) Kidney Function Test
7) Liver Function Test
8) Covid-19 RTPCR Test
9) Double-Marker
10) Hemogram
